If you’re a beauty lover, we’re willing to bet your Target runs always involves a pit stop at the beauty aisle. After all, the retailer is home to an impressive array of skin care, hair care and makeup brands — many of which we were surprised to find out call Target their home (MAC, anyone?). Whether you’re looking for a new brand to explore or are wanting to stock up on your tried-and-true favorites, we’ve rounded up 15 beauty brands available at Target we think you should keep an eye out for on your next shopping trip. HuffPost receives a share from retailers on this page. Every item is independently selected by the HuffPost Shopping team. Prices and availability are subject to change.